# Scattered Spider Detection Suite (KQL)

This directory contains detection logic inspired by real-world Scattered Spider activity. Each KQL script maps to a common tactic or technique from MITRE ATT&CK.

### Included Detections

- MFA Fatigue followed by Success
- Role Escalation to Admin
- New OAuth App Consent
- AADInternals Usage
- Inbox Rule Forwarding

> Focus: Azure AD, M365, Microsoft Defender

Use these detections alongside behavioral baselining and incident enrichment for better coverage of UNC3944 tradecraft.
